<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


知乎用户，<strong title="可怜的备胎柳，连那一点点可悲的快乐都像偷来的一样" class="zu-question-my-bio">可怜的备胎柳，连那一点点可悲的快乐都像…</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="887">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$huo-xing-46" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/huo-xing-46" class="zg-link" title="活性">活性</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$hai-dou-2-59" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/hai-dou-2-59" class="zg-link" title="海豆">海豆</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zhou-mao-12-23" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zhou-mao-12-23" class="zg-link" title="周猫">周猫</a></span>
