<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="4551711" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">许多年后，汤姆已经很老了，主人不再喜欢他，家里新来的猫咪也总是欺负他。当喵们再一次将汤姆的食物扔出门外时，汤姆拖着已不再灵便的腿走了好远，才将那块沾满灰尘的奶酪捡回来。他长舒了一口气，在喵们的嘲笑声中，小心翼翼的将奶酪放在墙角那个结满了蜘蛛网的老鼠洞门口(｡･ω･｡)ﾉ♡ <img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/a2943051b359e4c84685d478ceaebac8_b.jpg" data-rawheight="382" data-rawwidth="510" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="510" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/a2943051b359e4c84685d478ceaebac8_r.jpg"> 汤姆的不开心<img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/6465889b6acf252cdf8043f6e9ca98ad_b.jpg" data-rawheight="607" data-rawwidth="1080" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1080" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/6465889b6acf252cdf8043f6e9ca98ad_r.jpg"> 亦是杰瑞的不开心 <img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/5398db892125ed45aac93551fc724614_b.jpg" data-rawheight="607" data-rawwidth="1080" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1080" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/5398db892125ed45aac93551fc724614_r.jpg"><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/75f7df5081d27bc0bf29de0d45d3a934_b.jpg" data-rawheight="607" data-rawwidth="1080" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1080" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/75f7df5081d27bc0bf29de0d45d3a934_r.jpg"><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/b96088c268b77f2a7c3d8c93a08222ba_b.jpg" data-rawheight="607" data-rawwidth="1080" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1080" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/b96088c268b77f2a7c3d8c93a08222ba_r.jpg"> 汤姆你笑笑好不好，不要不理我π_π <img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/f842814f312ffd0c94ec54edff213ec0_b.jpg" data-rawheight="607" data-rawwidth="1080" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1080" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/f842814f312ffd0c94ec54edff213ec0_r.jpg"><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/65a8c2d23e659468a4617e9778b5d892_b.jpg" data-rawheight="607" data-rawwidth="1080" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1080" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/65a8c2d23e659468a4617e9778b5d892_r.jpg"><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/5b06887c5848499eafc4a5d4306aca28_b.jpg" data-rawheight="607" data-rawwidth="1080" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1080" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/5b06887c5848499eafc4a5d4306aca28_r.jpg"> 你拍一哇～我拍一～ <img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/07e434f03319f5c158fb6f234b12f9ea_b.jpg" data-rawheight="607" data-rawwidth="1080" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1080" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/07e434f03319f5c158fb6f234b12f9ea_r.jpg"><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/e5eccbf038100baf2ddfcf8b3f5a0ce7_b.jpg" data-rawheight="607" data-rawwidth="1080" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1080" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/e5eccbf038100baf2ddfcf8b3f5a0ce7_r.jpg"><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/088cbc3272876d17bf7991e3526b99cf_b.jpg" data-rawheight="607" data-rawwidth="1080" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1080" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/088cbc3272876d17bf7991e3526b99cf_r.jpg"><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/088cbc3272876d17bf7991e3526b99cf_b.jpg" data-rawheight="607" data-rawwidth="1080" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1080" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/088cbc3272876d17bf7991e3526b99cf_r.jpg"><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/1122735e8b4d687286cae321815c6b30_b.jpg" data-rawheight="607" data-rawwidth="1080" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1080" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/1122735e8b4d687286cae321815c6b30_r.jpg"><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/32d1cb6ee44d137db8c46cb416d1a709_b.jpg" data-rawheight="607" data-rawwidth="1080" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1080" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/32d1cb6ee44d137db8c46cb416d1a709_r.jpg"> 杰瑞快夸我(｡･ω･｡)ﾉ♡<img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/827bdf19c76af27fc1b0ce42bbbe2583_b.jpg" data-rawheight="607" data-rawwidth="1080" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1080" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/827bdf19c76af27fc1b0ce42bbbe2583_r.jpg"><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/704b642e128e37cdbbb7477df6603005_b.jpg" data-rawheight="607" data-rawwidth="1080" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1080" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/704b642e128e37cdbbb7477df6603005_r.jpg"><br><br><img src="/